h and full rebuild are distinct operations with different triggers — do not conflate them when advising operators.","Uncertainty and discarded reasoning paths may be noted in summaries but must not be presented as conclusions."]},"terminal_reason":"completed","fast_mode_state":"off","uuid":"75908e02-34ce-4e7b-b663-3084285c19ca"}
